UPDATE locales_quest SET offerrewardtext_loc8='Greetings young $C, I\'m glad to see you ready and eager to learn about the curing of poisons.$B$BWhile most druids in the past were put through pre-planned trials, your work will involve no such thing. There has been a rash of animal poisonings in Auberdine, and the village there has been unable to cure it. To that end, a representative there has asked Moonglade for aid and we are sending you there to aid them. This is no exercise - the work you\'ll do is quite real. Bear this in mind.' WHERE entry=6121;
